text:
The Russian Women's Football Championship (Russian: Чемпионат России по футболу среди женщин, "Chempionat Rossii po Futbolu credi zhenshchin") is the women's top division football league in Russia. The current champions are Zvezda Perm. Zvezda Perm has also won the most titles. The tournament was created in 1992.
